## 💾 STEP 5: Database Schema Update করুন

### MongoDB (Mongoose)
```javascript
// models/Message.js
const messageSchema = new Schema({
  chatId: String,
  userId: String,
  text: String,
  fileUrl: String,          // ✅ Cloudinary URL
  publicId: String,         // ✅ For deletion later
  fileName: String,
  fileSize: Number,
  createdAt: { type: Date, default: Date.now }
});

const userSchema = new Schema({
  email: String,
  profileImage: String,     // ✅ Cloudinary URL
  profileImagePublicId: String,
  documents: [
    {
      name: String,
      url: String,          // ✅ Cloudinary URL
      publicId: String,
      uploadedAt: Date
    }
  ]
});
```

### PostgreSQL (Prisma)
```prisma
// schema.prisma
model Message {
  id        Int     @id @default(autoincrement())
  chatId    Int
  userId    Int
  text      String?
  fileUrl   String?          // ✅ Cloudinary URL
  publicId  String?
  fileName  String?
  fileSize  Int?
  createdAt DateTime @default(now())
}

model User {
  id                  Int     @id @default(autoincrement())
  email               String  @unique
  profileImage        String?
  profileImagePublicId String?
  documents           Document[]
}

model Document {
  id        Int     @id @default(autoincrement())
  userId    Int
  user      User    @relation(fields: [userId], references: [id])
  name      String
  url       String              // ✅ Cloudinary URL
  publicId  String
  uploadedAt DateTime @default(now())
}
```

